node.text:
To all the fans out here at Spa and watching on TV around the world, we're sorry we couldn't put a show on for you.

We all wanted to see competitive and safe racing, but unfortunately this wasn't possible. Thanks for sticking with us.

See you in Zandvoort.

#FansLikeNoOther 🧡 #McLaren #F1 #BelgianGP
